name: K3 Fashion Party
overview: The girls from K3 want to have a dress up party, but their dress-up box is empty! Can you help the girls with filling their dress-up box so they can have their party? K3 Fashion Party guarantees many hours of fun, and includes K3 hits like MaMaSé!, Kuma He, Alle Kleuren, Hallo K3 and of course their latest single Eyo!
